prompts.frontCover: A dreamy fantasy anime-style 2D illustration of a beautiful, slightly bewildered fairy queen, representing Lao Lao, with flowing pastel hair adorned with glowing flowers. She is sitting majestically on a throne made of giant, stacked macarons in soft pink, lavender, and mint green. Two chubby, chibi-style unicorns with rainbow manes are playfully trying to steal a giant, sparkling birthday cake from her lap, their expressions mischievous. The background is a magical, enchanted forest clearing at twilight, with glowing mushrooms, whimsical flora, and sparkling fireflies dotting the air. In the center, in an elegant, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday to my Queen, Lao Lao".
